  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Eden is only 120 metres form Sirmione's stunning castle and a few steps from its many shops, bars and restaurants. It's got a harbour front location with amazing views over the lake. Head for the terrace with a drink or grab a lounger on the bathing platform to enjoy the best views.</p>]]></listingDescription>
