  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms</strong> are about 19m² and sleep two people. They're furnished in a contemporary style and have air conditioning, TV, safe, minibar, hairdryer and a bath or shower. </p>
<p><strong>Quality Rooms</strong> are the same size and have balconies. Some of these rooms have full lake views while others have partial views of the lake through the trees. </p>
<p><strong>Classic Rooms for Sole Use</strong> are available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
